            Fully committed to <span class="text-[var(--base09)]">NixOS</span> for system configuration. Built a <span class="text-[var(--base0D)]">4-host mining cluster</span> with Colmena deployment, currently migrating to Kubernetes. Developing production apps with <span class="text-[var(--base09)]">Rust microservices</span>, <span class="text-[var(--base0D)]">React frontends</span>, and <span class="text-[var(--base09)]">AI integration</span>.
